Description: A modified version of PRISMA2020 v1.1.4 with fixes for:
    hardcoded label suppression (no forced "Records identified from:" or
    "(n = 0)" when data is empty), detail data proper formatting, and
    dummy default removal. Original by Haddaway et al. (2022).
